name: Smolest Chimney
description: This is smol version of my photograph "Simple Chimney 3" taken back in 2018 on my island Paxos. I like looking up when i am walking home. I like looking at the old chimneys and how some have kept a certain style or work. Traditional art was manifested usually through common things that were used in the house or displayed on it. Chimneys were and still are like that. 16x16px
